## Summary Statistics

```{r cars}
mtcars %>% 
    gather(key="variable",value=value) %>% 
    group_by(variable) %>% 
    summarize(mean=mean(value,na.rm=T),
              sd=sd(value,na.rm=T)) %>% 
    datatable() %>% 
    formatRound(columns=c("mean","sd"),digits=3)
    
```
